-get dist-upgrade<\/em><\/p>\n<p>1. Kubuntu-devel mailing list: <a href=\"https:\/\/lists.ubuntu.com\/mailman\/listinfo\/kubuntu-devel\">https:\/\/lists.ubuntu.com\/mailman\/listinfo\/kubuntu-devel<\/a><br \/>\n2. Kubuntu IRC channels: #kubuntu &amp; #kubuntu-devel on irc.freenode.net<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Since we missed by a whisker getting updated PIM (kontact, kmail, akregator, kgpg etc..) into Zesty for release day, and we believe it is important that our users have access to this significant update, packages are now available for testers in the Kubuntu backports landing ppa. While we believe these&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":144,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[129,243],"tags":[249,155,251],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/kubuntu.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3173"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/kubuntu.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/kubuntu.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/kubuntu.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/144"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/kubuntu.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=3173"}],"version-history":[{"count":10,"href":"https:\/\/kubuntu.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3173\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":3185,"href":"https:\/\/kubuntu.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3173\/revisions\/3185"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/kubuntu.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=3173"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/kubuntu.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=3173"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/kubuntu.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=3173"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}